Bellows Falls Savings Institution v. Garrie S. French.Appeal from Superior Court of Cook County.Stillman & Hartyn, attorneys for appellant.S. A. French, attorney for appellee; Gage & Deming, of counsel.

Ho questions are involved in this appeal, except the sufficiency of the proof to sustain the allegations of a cross-bill, which was heretofore considered by this court in 67 Ill. App. 179. Opinion not reported.
